1 polymer     syn GLY-GLY-TYR-ASN-LEU-ARG-PRO-ARG-THR-TYR-GLN-PRO-GLN-ARG-TYR-GLY-GLY-GLY 2043.228  1 ? ? ? 
;The peptide is connected at the N-terminus to a long polyethylene glycol linker, which is in turn connected to a gold(I)-based compound [Au(4-diphenylphosphanyl-benzoic acid)Cl]. Only the peptide, GGYNLRPRTYQPQRYGG (C-terminal G has an amide group in place of the carboxylate group), is incorporated into the model.
